| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7561 — Recovery Inhibition (nova)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0eca2679-1fc7-53c3-bb55-e7c0cbf705f8"
